text: in today's fast-paced world everyone has
places to be but not enough time in
their jam-packed schedules introducing
wild ride a new Innovative unicorn
transportation service that helps people
get to their destination faster and
hasslefree you simply open the wild
rides app request a unicorn and then
wait for the nearest unicorn to arrive
and pick you up it's better faster safer
and more magical with fresh Venture
Capital funding wild rides is seeking
talented engineers like you to help
build its platform using Amazon web
services wild rides technology platform
will be built using serverless
architectures with services like AWS
Lambda which let you run code without
provisioning or managing servers hop on
board and help wild rides build the
future of magical Transportation by
joining one of our free guided workshops
in a city near you
